defaultLondon Councils is a cross-party organisation, representing London’s 32 boroughs
default and the 
defaultCity of London.  
defaultThe London Procurement Strategy Board (LPSB) is the principal, strategic procurement board for London local government.  It brings together senior finance and procurement officers to develop and deliver a procurement strategy for London local government.  
